  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n1. open status\r\n2. click I dont have other device and import a seed phrase\r\n3. when being on the Fetching data screen, resize it a bit (or open on small laptop like mine, 13 inch)\r\n4. try to scroll to the Continue button\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** \r\n\r\n1. continue button is overlapped with fetching data details\r\n2. scrolling to the button is not possbile\r\n3. the screen is not autoresizing components to adjust different screen sizes\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1552\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-06-06 at 10 17 12\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/82375995/5af40621-6350-42b3-a8d2-da7305e4d5fe\">\r\n",
